Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（OP）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了一個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的激烈 殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.83,0:00:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.52,0:00:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我一直注視著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本機即將到達失落大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是日本國內首個設立的獨立自治區
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.59,0:00:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正實行著特別保護法 被許可的遙遠的那裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且作為分身士的生存地點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時隔七年的失落大陸...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我好好望風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦 我們在幹著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面 從上面來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.61,0:01:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.44,0:01:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是白癡麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 快跑 別過來...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然工作還算輕鬆 不過這大叔真夠沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}用我這隻手奪取一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}即使心靈受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}覺醒的本能不斷驅使著身體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}語言能改變本義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}昨天的真實 今天就變成了謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:03:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}誰都只能在彷徨中搖曳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,300)}夢想和愛等等不過是作為托詞的美妙幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}進入現實 則沒有結果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}伸出手把握明天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Reckless fire 如此大膽地點燃了靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}無處可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}與將謊言和矛盾一飲而盡的力量一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}現在不奢望 深藏在彼此心中的 Sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}不交給任何人 直到我掌握到了某樣東西...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對像估計在等級E以上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(330,450,496,450,0,1500)}{\fad(1500,1500)}一  馬
