Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查時請絕對小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這慘狀是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身士出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都認真學過的不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查分身士犯罪的工作是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,習慣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我們警察在這種時候只能在旁邊幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 長官呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒有什麼外傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出重要人物 掃蕩危險分子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來交給專家就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專家是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險分子什麼的愛怎樣怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現在現場的分身士的目擊證詞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據報告 嫌疑犯是徒手的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒手？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是..是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌疑犯利用成田機場的特別第47班飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那樣從上空落下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垂直一線落到現場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒用降落傘...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈 哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身士還真是單刀直入哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像我們的立浪一樣 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有新情報
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請通知聖堂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs18}聖堂(HOLY)：本土在失落大陸設立的武裝警察機關HOLD，\N在其中專門設置針對分身能力犯罪者的作戰部隊,其成員部分為分身士。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈 不要這麼僵硬嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說你很僵硬麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 新來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個年紀和經驗...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是分身士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用外表判斷這裡的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要當成他們全部都有分身士的危險性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身士只有分身士能對付的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不是本土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於22年前的大隆起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被徹底損毀的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去咯 回去咯...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡 再往右點 右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕鬆鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是輕鬆的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前暫時不用受失業之苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 一馬 又去打架了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是工作啊 工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別騙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比平常還多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救人的報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會去幹了什麼危險的勾當了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你一個人嗎 爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在工地受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在家裏睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸帥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡你爸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:06:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油工作哦 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有資格說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 要付多少...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少3塊錢 不賒帳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多給點大哥哥會更高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(500,173)}將笑容還給這片大地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(558,217)}日本政府
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出長官的是原始分身士麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據謝莉絲的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多此一舉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴伊麗安 不能放任原始的分身士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:07:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚藍的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像能踫到一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還沒回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 已經第三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底有沒有好好工作...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能性是一半一半
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去我家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請你喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 我來泡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 拜託別那樣叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明擺著嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別老不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要吃飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 下次再去喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 一君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都讓你別這麼叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 呀 這個吶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼 讓我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到一半的時候還很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我一不留神就被扣錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是幹不長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒出息 幹了也白幹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被說成廢物也行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米和菜都沒多少了 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得真的很糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵 喲 還好不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹啥 快滾回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嗎突然這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:09:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別從那進來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再拿些飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 一馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道拉達斯那個組織麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在地鐵那裏盤踞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的是秀樹那幫人吧 盡是些小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們那裏 有別的組織找他們去挑釁了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的頭目是個分身士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我去救場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵 就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方也是分身士的話 出什麼事我可不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹也不是不認識的外人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩千元就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就三十
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你把價錢放太低了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你抬太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊 你今早的工作不是挺不錯的來著麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒了就是沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又那麼幹了 一馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君島 要不要吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想吃白食嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩千
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從伊利亞那裏傳來了感應報告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是斑馬43
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原始分身士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留她一個人在家沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:11:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她比外表看起來堅強多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是兄妹對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啦 快去暴打他們一頓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上果然冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本土有一直跟夏天似的的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 為什麼沒在那種地方出生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種地方是無憂無慮的和平世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會無聊死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的... 你個血氣方剛的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是比夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我聽好 這的古董都是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快給我從這裡滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小鬼怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:12:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你喜歡哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片地盤...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止 這破車
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想那樣 這是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作前就把我搞累了怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們兩個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷來的車 別計較太多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一...一馬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起我們來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 傳說中的分身士在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩千
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就三十
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就兩千兩百
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還加錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要算上伙食費
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃了那麼多本就該付錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失算了 很漂亮的一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比夫開始笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快離開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是快喚出分身比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼輸了你會後悔的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 居然敢這麼對待比夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 不要輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一對一決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一馬 接下來別被反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放手一搏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我喚出分身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喚出分身的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 比夫要喚出分身了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 看我打得你粉身碎骨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我的車子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正樹 讓大家逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後悔了吧 這就是我的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨錘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了 他燃起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開 開玩笑吧 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 接下來輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有分身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違的分身戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得充滿幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生下來就擁有奇怪的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能享受這種感覺也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身能力也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也這麼想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小分身算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 快放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱智
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說你是弱智嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 讓我再多享受點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.47,0:17:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也很無聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏 逃到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一馬 那種小角色快點解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看清楚咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼才是真正的分身士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝擊的第一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的分身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比夫 比夫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢把比夫...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要打嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打的話 就讓我們來當對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原始分身士君～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加裝消音器多少準備好掃蕩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一馬 不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是聖堂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四千
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出四千我就幫你爭取時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也快滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有地方抓我可不管
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融合體類型
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 就是早上那個單純笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再讓你們多活幾分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 想打
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗毛孔都張開了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這感覺到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這狀況會非常的糟糕
